OL,3,CDebbie Leitch looked 'like a skeleton'
OL,4,Cbefore neglect death
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of disabled
OL,7,Fwoman Debbie Leitch in Blackpool has
OL,8,Fheard harrowing details of the
OL,9,Fconditions in which she spent her
OL,10,Ffinal days.
OL,12,FDebbie, 24 who who was born with
OL,13,FDown's syndrome, was discovered dead
OL,14,Fat her family home in Blackpool in
OL,15,FAugust 2019. She weighed under four
OL,16,Fstone at the time and had been
OL,17,Fabandoned by her mother to die alone,
OL,18,Fin pain and in squalid conditions.
