OL,3,CDebbie Leitch looked 'like a skeleton'
OL,4,Cbefore neglect death
OL,6,FElaine Clarke, 49, was jailed for nine
OL,7,Fyears and seven months after pleading
OL,8,Fguilty to gross negligence
OL,9,Fmanslaughter after she initially
OL,10,Fdenied the offence.
OL,12,FA five day inquest which started
OL,13,FMonday 14 October heard a written
OL,14,Fstatement from a former carer who
OL,15,Fvisited the family home to attend to a
OL,16,Fdifferent matter.
