OL,3,CDebbie Leitch looked 'like a skeleton'
OL,4,Cbefore neglect death
OL,6,FScott Worthington, a former carer with
OL,7,FCherish UK, described how he felt that
OL,8,Fthe mother didn't care for her family
OL,9,Fcalling the environment 'very dirty'
OL,10,Fand how there was 'chaos' in the
OL,11,Fhousehold.
OL,13,FMr Worthington also described hearing
OL,14,F'loud crying from a room upstairs' and
OL,15,Fon the one occasion he saw Ms Leitch
OL,16,Fin person, he was shocked by her
OL,17,Fappearance saying she was gaunt and
OL,18,F'looked like a skeleton'.
