OL,3,CDebbie Leitch looked 'like a skeleton'
OL,4,Cbefore neglect death
OL,6,FCoroner, Alan Wilson also heard a
OL,7,Fwritten statement from another former
OL,8,Fcarer, Solomon Thornton who again
OL,9,Fvisited the house to deal with another
OL,10,Fmatter. Mr Thornton described finding
OL,11,F"bottles filled with urine" in the
OL,12,Fhouse and "always stacks of dirty pots
OL,13,Fin the kitchen".
OL,15,FMr Thornton also recalled hearing loud
OL,16,Fcrying coming from a room upstairs and
OL,17,Fhow the house had a strong smell of
OL,18,Ffaeces.
